# 定义环境变量
@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:8080
@token = 1234567890
@adminToken = YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE
@userToken = YOUR_USER_TOKEN_HERE

### ==================== 认证接口 ====================

### 1. 用户注册
# @name register
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser11",
  "password": "123456",
  "name": "测试管理员1",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "role": "ADMIN"
}

### 2. 用户登录
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testadmin",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 3. 登出
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. 登录 - 错误密码
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "password": "wrongpassword"
}

### 5. 登录 - 不存在的用户
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "nonexistent",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 6. 注册 - 用户名已存在
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "password": "123456",
  "name": "重复用户",
  "email": "duplicate@example.com"
}

### 7. 注册 - 缺少必填字段
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "incomplete",
  "password": "123456"
}

### ==================== 基础 CRUD ====================

### 1. 获取用户列表（分页）
GET {{baseUrl}}/user/page?pageNo=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2. 创建新用户
# @name createUser
POST {{baseUrl}}/user
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Alice",
  "age": 18
}

### 3. 更新用户（需先获取version）
PUT {{baseUrl}}/user
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "id": 1,
  "name": "Alice Updated",
  "age": 20,
  "version": 1
}

### 4. 删除用户（逻辑删除）
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/user/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5. 条件搜索
GET {{baseUrl}}/user/search?name=Alice&age=18
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ==================== 高级查询 ====================

### 6. 分页 + 模糊搜索姓名
GET {{baseUrl}}/user/page?pageNo=1&pageSize=5&name=Ali
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 7. 分页 + 年龄筛选
GET {{baseUrl}}/user/page?pageNo=1&pageSize=10&age=25
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 8. 分页 + 时间范围
GET {{baseUrl}}/user/page?pageNo=1&pageSize=10&start=2026-04-14T00:00:00&end=2026-04-15T23:59:59
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ==================== 边界与异常测试 ====================

### 9. 创建用户 - 空姓名
POST {{baseUrl}}/user
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "",
  "age": 25
}

### 10. 创建用户 - 缺少年龄字段
POST {{baseUrl}}/user
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "NoAge"
}

### 11. 分页 - 越界页码
GET {{baseUrl}}/user/page?pageNo=999&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 12. 更新 - 不存在 ID
PUT {{baseUrl}}/user
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "id": 9999,
  "name": "Ghost",
  "age": 30,
  "version": 1
}

### 13. 删除 - 不存在的记录
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/user/9999
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ==================== 并发与乐观锁测试 ====================

### 14. 并发修改模拟（乐观锁冲突）
# 步骤 A：先读取用户数据，记录 version
GET {{baseUrl}}/user/search?name=Alice
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 步骤 B：用旧 version 更新（模拟冲突，预期返回 false）
PUT {{baseUrl}}/user
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "id": 1,
  "name": "Conflict Update",
  "age": 99,
  "version": 0
}

### ==================== 组合业务场景 ====================

### 15. 创建后查询验证
# @name createAndVerify
POST {{baseUrl}}/user
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "VerifyMe",
  "age": 22
}

### 验证刚才创建的用户
GET {{baseUrl}}/user/search?name=VerifyMe
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 16. 批量操作后查询总数
# 先创建多条数据
### 创建用户 1
POST {{baseUrl}}/user
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Batch_1",
  "age": 20
}

### 创建用户 2
POST {{baseUrl}}/user
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Batch_2",
  "age": 21
}

### 查看分页总数是否增加
GET {{baseUrl}}/user/page?pageNo=1&pageSize=100
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ==================== 性能观察 ====================

### 17. 空条件查询 - 观察响应时间
GET {{baseUrl}}/user/page?pageNo=1&pageSize=1000
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 18. 精确匹配 - 高选择性查询
GET {{baseUrl}}/user/search?name=ExactMatch
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ==================== 文件上传权限测试 ====================

### 19. 通用文件上传 - 使用 ADMIN Token（应该成功）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/files/upload?subDir=documents
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebAppBoundary
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="test.txt"
Content-Type: text/plain

This is a test file.
--WebAppBoundary--

### 20. 通用文件上传 - 使用 USER Token（应该成功，USER 有 user:upload 权限）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/files/upload?subDir=documents
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebAppBoundary
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="test.txt"
Content-Type: text/plain

This is a test file.
--WebAppBoundary--

### 21. 删除文件 - 使用 ADMIN Token（应该成功）
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/files/delete?filePath=/uploads/documents/test.txt
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 22. 删除文件 - 使用 USER Token（应该失败，USER 没有 user:delete 权限）
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/files/delete?filePath=/uploads/documents/test.txt
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}
